                         - How to install ProNET -

@{" Making a Parallel Cable   " LINK CABLE} The parallel connection cable
@{" AmigaDOS                  " LINK INTER} Always useful to know

@{" pronet.device             " LINK INSTALL_DEV} The basic transfer routines
